{"title":"博客的诞生","date":"2018-06-12T08:37:56.000Z","link":"post/博客的诞生","comments":true,"tags":["Hexo"],"categories":["技术"],"updated":"2019-11-26T07:32:01.382Z","content":"<h1 id=\"简介\">简介<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#简介\"></a></h1><p>一款完全属于自己的博客，所用技术：<code>nodeJs</code>，<code>git</code>，<code>hexo</code></p>\n<h1 id=\"hexo-本地配置\">hexo 本地配置<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#hexo-本地配置\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"安装-hexo\">安装 hexo<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#安装-hexo\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir hexo &amp;&amp; cd hexo</span><br><span class=\"line\">cnpm i hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class=\"line\">cnpm i hexo --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"检测是否安装成功\">检测是否安装成功<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#检测是否安装成功\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"初始化\">初始化<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#初始化\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"安装依赖包\">安装依赖包<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#安装依赖包\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cnpm i</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"首次体验-hexo\">首次体验 hexo<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#首次体验-hexo\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">清除冗余代码，必要时使用</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo clean</span><br><span class=\"line\">编译</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo g</span><br><span class=\"line\">启动服务器</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>此时在浏览器输入 <code>localhost:4000</code> 就可看到自己的博客啦</p>\n<h2 id=\"发布\">发布<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#发布\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">需提前安装一个扩展</span><br><span class=\"line\">cnpm i hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class=\"line\">再发布</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo d -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>此时在浏览器输入 <code>自己在 git 上设置的博客地址</code> 就可看到自己的博客啦</p>\n<h2 id=\"新建博客\">新建博客<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#新建博客\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new 博客名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"新建文件夹\">新建文件夹<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#新建文件夹\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new page 博客名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"将-hexo-与-github-page-联系起来\">将 hexo 与 github page 联系起来<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#将-hexo-与-github-page-联系起来\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"配置-git-个人信息\">配置 git 个人信息<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#配置-git-个人信息\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git config --global urser.name \"zine-fj\"</span><br><span class=\"line\">git config --global user.email \"747810974@qq.com\"</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">生成秘钥</span><br><span class=\"line\">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C \"747810974@qq.com\"</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"配置-Deployment\">配置 Deployment<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#配置-Deployment\"></a></h3><p>在hexo根目录中的 _config.yml，找到Deployment，然后操作如下:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  type: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  repo: git@github.com:yourname/yourname.github.io.git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"主题配置\">主题配置<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#主题配置\"></a></h1><p>将所用到的主题下载到 <code>根文件</code> 里面的 <code>theme</code>中，然后在 <code>根文件</code> 的 <code>_config.yml</code> 中配置</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">theme: inside</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"主题推荐\">主题推荐<a href=\"post/博客的诞生#主题推荐\"></a></h1><ul>\n<li>最经典主题 <code>next</code>：<a href=\"https://notes.iissnan.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">next</a></li>\n<li>比较清新的一款主题 <code>Yilia</code>：<a href=\"http://litten.me/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Yilia</a></li>\n<li>很像网页的一款主题 <code>skapp</code>：<a href=\"http://blog.minfive.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">skapp</a></li>\n<li>卡片化较多的一款主题 <code>matery</code>: <a href=\"https://blinkfox.github.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">matery</a><br>…  </li>\n<li>目前最看上眼的主题 <code>inside</code>: <a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">inside</a></li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"博客在不同电脑异步问题","link":"post/博客在不同电脑异步问题"},"next":{"title":"心生七面 善恶难辨","link":"post/心生七面-善恶难辨"},"plink":"https://zine-fj.github.io/blog/post/博客的诞生/","toc":[{"title":"简介","id":"简介","index":"1"},{"title":"hexo 本地配置","id":"hexo-本地配置","index":"2","children":[{"title":"安装 hexo","id":"安装-hexo","index":"2.1"},{"title":"检测是否安装成功","id":"检测是否安装成功","index":"2.2","children":[{"title":"初始化","id":"初始化","index":"2.2.1"},{"title":"安装依赖包","id":"安装依赖包","index":"2.2.2"},{"title":"首次体验 hexo","id":"首次体验-hexo","index":"2.2.3"}]},{"title":"发布","id":"发布","index":"2.3"},{"title":"新建博客","id":"新建博客","index":"2.4"},{"title":"新建文件夹","id":"新建文件夹","index":"2.5"},{"title":"将 hexo 与 github page 联系起来","id":"将-hexo-与-github-page-联系起来","index":"2.6","children":[{"title":"配置 git 个人信息","id":"配置-git-个人信息","index":"2.6.1"},{"title":"配置 Deployment","id":"配置-Deployment","index":"2.6.2"}]}]},{"title":"主题配置","id":"主题配置","index":"3"},{"title":"主题推荐","id":"主题推荐","index":"4"}]}